  "title": "Finance Intern",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><ul><li>Manage financial and investment portfolios for corporate businesses (B2B) and individual clients (B2C) on Investment, Risk and Asset Management.</li><li>Analyse financial markets and investment funds such as Equities, ETFs, Bonds and Unit Trusts.</li><li>Provide integrated financial solutions for clients through Wealth Preservation, Partnership Management, Estate and Business Succession Planning.</li><li>Develop business strategies based on current market developments to grow clients' portfolios</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Type</strong></u></p><ul><li>Entry level position. Full-time and part-time positions available.</li><li>Open to Undergraduates and Fresh Graduates.</li><li>Flexible working hours, work from home option available.</li><li><u>No</u> prior experience in Finance or Investment required.</li></ul>",
